{
  "name": "RPlog_Bean_Spilling",
  "title": "Bean Spilling at the Grand Palanhi",
  "summary": "Chasing after the bolting youngster Shenner outside the Palanhi City Starport, Major Jessalyn coaxes the frightened kid into a drink at the casino of the Grand Palanhi Hotel. Over rounds of Corellian brandy, both drunk and confiding, Shenner unburdens her past as a whore's daughter with an Imperial father, her flight from Tatooine and a Corellian who saw through her disguise as a boy, while Jessalyn pours out her own anguish over loving Luke Skywalker. Their tearful heart-to-heart is interrupted when Shenner's employer Grathix arrives and tries to drag the inebriated girl away, prompting Jessalyn to draw her blaster and call Luke for help. When Grathix abruptly discovers that Shenner is in fact a girl and freezes in shock, Jessalyn hauls Shenner back to the ship Black Dragon, where the kid finally passes out in the older woman's arms.",
